# Override the parent integ .gitignore (which ignores all *.js) so the Docker
# image asset's source file is tracked. The Dockerfile builds against
# ${LAMBDA_TASK_ROOT}/app.js and the AWS Lambda Node.js base image's RIE
# entrypoint expects the .js extension. (The Python zip-asset Lambdas need no
# override — only *.js is ignored.)
!docker/*.js
!docker/Dockerfile
